That’s why we created a warm, welcoming space where friends become family, the food feels both comforting and crave-worthy, and every guest’s voice truly matters. We’re not just a pub—we’re The People’s Pub . A place to gather, share stories, raise a glass, and create memories together. More stores you might like Chicken Salad Chick Craving healthy food that’s full of flavor? At Chicken Salad Chick of Seminole , we serve up fresh, made-from-scratch entrées that never compromise on taste. Every visit comes with a warm welcome and a generous helping of Southern hospitality. From sweet to spicy, classic to savory, our chicken salad flavors cover the whole spectrum—so there’s something for everyone. And if chicken salad isn’t your go-to, don’t worry—we’ve got sandwiches, crisp salads, and other delicious options to please even the pickiest eaters. Come hungry, leave happy. At Chipotle, we’re on a mission to cultivate a better world. That means making wholesome, classic-cooked meals more accessible to everyone, while leading the way in digital innovation, sustainable business practices, and purposeful brand initiatives. Real food. Real ingredients. Real easy. Applebee's Make Applebee’s your go-to neighborhood bar and grill . Whether you’re grabbing an affordable lunch with coworkers or enjoying a delicious dinner with family and friends , Applebee’s offers flavorful dining options everyone will love . Be sure to ask about happy hour and explore our wide selection of beers, cocktails, and beverages to quench your thirst. Call ahead at (727) 258-7079 to see what’s on tap today and plan your next visit! Cava At CAVA , flavor’s in your hands. Create grain bowls, salads, and pitas with bold flavors to fuel your fullest life. CAVA started in a chef’s kitchen, and the restaurant’s first-generation-Greek founders remain committed to thoughtful cooking, vibrant ingredients, and innovative twists throughout the menu. Get the CAVA app, order ahead, and earn rewards every time the craving strikes. CAVA is grounded in the Mediterranean way of life , where food is at the center of culture and connection. They are inspired by our Mediterranean roots, where deliciousness and health are inseparable. Sacrificing health for flavor? Or flavor for health? Not at CAVA—no compromises here.
